that he was prepared,

123
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,600
and not a single official was injured.

124
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:57,200
- Not a single one?
- Yes.

125
00:14:58,200 --> 00:15:00,640
I'm afraid
that even if there were casualties,

126
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:02,840
he wouldn't dare let me know.

127
00:15:02,920 --> 00:15:04,040
Besides,

128
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:07,080
the one accompanying him into the Capital
wasn't Shi Yan, but Zhong Lin.

129
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:10,560
She must be coming to see Cangcang, right?

130
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:13,640
It's fine.

131
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:16,960
It's about time
Cangcang saw an old friend.

132
00:15:17,040 --> 00:15:19,800
WUYING HALL

133
00:15:25,520 --> 00:15:26,520
Preceptor Du.

134
00:15:30,640 --> 00:15:31,560
Eunuch Feng.

135
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,960
May I ask

136
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:36,920
where His Majesty has just come back from?

137
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:38,560
Linghe Hall.

138
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:50,600
I can manage on my own. I'm fine.

139
00:15:51,280 --> 00:15:53,960
His Majesty specifically instructed us
to be extra careful with your right arm.

140
00:15:54,560 --> 00:15:55,880
So, please let me serve you.

141
00:16:01,680 --> 00:16:03,000
Is His Majesty

142
00:16:03,640 --> 00:16:04,760
all right?

143
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:06,560
His Majesty missed his medicine,

144
00:16:06,640 --> 00:16:08,800
then spent his inner strength
purging the poison from you,

145
00:16:08,880 --> 00:16:10,240
and even took a sword strike from you.

146
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:11,600
His condition is very serious.

147
00:16:12,920 --> 00:16:14,880
Your Majesty, Preceptor Du barged in…

148
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:18,160
Du Tingxin of Nanrong Palace
pays respects to Your Majesty.

149
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,280
Rise, Preceptor Du.

150
00:16:24,680 --> 00:16:25,720
Leave it to me.

151
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:30,680
Xiaoshan, you all may go.

152
00:16:31,280 --> 00:16:32,520
- Got it.
- Got it.

153
00:16:40,560 --> 00:16:42,480
You came in person.

154
00:16:42,560 --> 00:16:45,320
Something major happened the day
before yesterday?

155
00:16:47,400 --> 00:16:50,320
You were controlled
by Princess Ying's Puppet Incense

156
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:52,920
and tried to stab His Majesty.

157
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:59,600
But you dislocated your own arm

158
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:02,200
to keep His Majesty safe.

159
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:14,079
You came in person just to tell me this?

160
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:17,000
Your Majesty is perceptive.

161
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:20,640
Then I won't hide anything.

162
00:17:23,319 --> 00:17:24,560
Are you aware

163
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:26,319
of my background?

164
00:17:27,440 --> 00:17:28,280
Please enlighten me.

165
00:17:30,360 --> 00:17:33,360
I'm the former Preceptor's daughter,
not her disciple.

166
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:37,800
An Imperial Preceptor
was supposed to live a spotless life.

167
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:41,920
But she had an affair with another man
and secretly gave birth to me.

168
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:45,280
She raised me as her "disciple".

169
00:17:48,560 --> 00:17:49,880
Later, when the truth came out,

170
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:53,560
my mother was forced
to burn herself alive to atone.

171
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:57,160
Her only wish was to keep me safe.

172
00:17:58,640 --> 00:18:00,000
But the ministers

173
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:02,160
still wouldn't let it go.

174
00:18:05,120 --> 00:18:06,920
<i>I was hiding in the shrine that day.</i>

175
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:08,240
<i>This girl</i>

176
00:18:08,320 --> 00:18:10,880
<i>is an affront to Heaven and our ancestors.</i>

177
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:12,560
<i>She has no right to live.</i>

178
00:18:13,080 --> 00:18:14,440
<i>She should be sacrificed to Heaven!</i>

179
00:18:35,880 --> 00:18:36,760
Don't be afraid.

180
00:18:37,280 --> 00:18:39,880
Today, I exercised my right to pardon.

181
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:41,400
From this day on,

182
00:18:41,480 --> 00:18:42,720
you are the new Imperial Preceptor.

183
00:18:42,800 --> 00:18:44,640
Why did my master

184
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:47,800
name the shrine "Nanrong Palace"?

185
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:49,400
Did she think

186
00:18:49,480 --> 00:18:51,680
I was unwelcome to the world?

187
00:18:51,760 --> 00:18:53,000
Even if the world rejects you,

188
00:18:53,080 --> 00:18:55,040
you must fight to live.

189
00:18:55,560 --> 00:18:57,520
The former Preceptor burned herself alive.

190
00:18:57,600 --> 00:19:00,000
Isn't this the very result she sought?

191
00:19:14,240 --> 00:19:15,800
<i>That day, when His Majesty took my hand</i>

192
00:19:17,320 --> 00:19:18,840
and led me out of Nanrong Palace,

193
00:19:21,080 --> 00:19:22,480
I made up my mind

194
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:26,920
that my whole life
would belong to him alone.

195
00:19:32,360 --> 00:19:34,200
If His Majesty can be
with the one he loves,

196
00:19:35,040 --> 00:19:36,320
that is the greatest joy I could ask for.

197
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:40,680
You don't actually think

198
00:19:40,760 --> 00:19:42,840
the one His Majesty loves is me, do you?

199
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:46,600
Why are you so certain it isn't?

200
00:19:55,720 --> 00:19:57,040
Emperors are heartless.

201
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:59,000
In the end,

202
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:01,200
power is all he's ever valued.

203
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:05,040
I came here today

204
00:20:06,160 --> 00:20:08,040
because the night before last,

205
00:20:08,120 --> 00:20:09,640
you were under someone else's control,

206
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:12,600
yet you chose to injure yourself
rather than harm His Majesty.

207
00:20:13,600 --> 00:20:14,680
I believe

208
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:17,400
Your Majesty

209
00:20:18,120 --> 00:20:19,760
might truly care for him after all.

210
00:20:32,520 --> 00:20:35,120
I beg Your Majesty
to give His Majesty a little trust.

211
00:20:36,280 --> 00:20:38,720
If affection can grow between you,

212
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:40,080
then Nanrong Palace

213
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:43,000
will be Linghe Hall's most loyal ally.

214
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,400
And if I can't?

215
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:52,360
I should say no more.

216
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:54,360
Such words would be overstepping.

217
00:20:58,200 --> 00:20:59,560
Your Majesty is still recovering,

218
00:21:00,240 --> 00:21:01,360
so I will take my leave.

219
